Unified MESGTs
with symmetric target spaces 



In this paper, we are interested in 'unified'
 Maxwell-Einstein supergravity
theories, in which a simple global symmetry group acts irreducibly 
on all 
the vector fields .


In general, the global symmetries of a 5D, 
MESGT can be divided into two categories:
 
Any  MESGT is always
invariant under the global R-symmetry
group . As mentioned earlier,   acts nontrivially only
on the fermions  and
